 omits), purely functional via `dataclasses.replace` with positive non-mutation tests (D mutates in place), single difficulty table, `rng=None` → module `random`, and tests that import the message constants and build fixtures directly.\n\n**Verdict: ADOPT C.**\n\n**Distilled to `.code-tips.md`:** one new rule — *a game-ending state transition MUST overwrite `status_message` with the terminal (win/loss) text naming the word, and tests must assert that exact message, not just flags* — plus a caller contract for `apply_guess` (reassign; don't assume purity). Appended this round's reconfirmation provenance to the positive-assertion, message-constants, single-config-table, and direct-fixture rules.\n\nArtifacts written: `blind-sketch.md`, `review.md`, `verdict.json`, and the `.code-tips.md` updates. Nothing staged or committed."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":605,"cache_read_input_tokens":122414,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":605},"output_tokens":3,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"26931df1-8f61-42b8-a8d5-65221b0797a9","uuid":"1bfe4721-f666-481d-868c-b550a8bb2ee5","request_id":"req_011CbxfyPpNyZjh9Vxnq4gp1"},{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"api_error_status":null,"duration_ms":474469,"duration_api_ms":475588,"ttft_ms":6763,"ttft_stream_ms":2021,"time_to_request_ms":31,"num_turns":58,"result":"Review complete. All scratch worktrees removed; the worker worktrees and dispatch logs (`task-001-w*`, `w*.stdout/stderr`) were left untouched and unread per the anonymity rules.\n\n## Summary\n\nI followed the protocol in order: wrote a **blind sketch** before opening any diff, read SPEC + `.code-tips.md`, then verified all five candidates empirically in scratch worktrees at base `712c2a9`.\n\n**Gate results:** all five p